  <Subject Subject_ID="300006343">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300006335</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>food processing plants [300006335], processing plants [300164121], factories by function [300006238], factories (structures) [300006232], industrial buildings [300006231], industrial structures [300121918], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings built after the early 19th century, not found only on farms, for the mechanized processing, storing, or selling of milk and milk products. Distinguished from "dairies (non-mechanized)" by the use of mechanization. For subsidiary agricultural buildings devoted primarily to the care of milk, often with little or no mechanization, prefer "milk houses."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Edificio construido después de los inicios del siglo XIX, que no se encuentra únicamente en las granjas, destinado al procesamiento mecanizado, al almacenaje o a la venta de leche y sus productos derivados. Se diferencia de "lechería (no mecanizada)" por el uso de mecanización. Para edificios agícolas subsidiarios dedicados principalmente al cuidado de la leche, frecuentemente con una pequeña o ninguna mecanización, prefiera "lechería".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor gebouwen die na het begin van de 19e eeuw werden gebouwd, en niet alleen op boerderijen, voor het gemechaniseerd verwerken, bewaren of verkopen van melk en melkproducten. Te onderscheiden van 'zuivelbedrijven' door de mechanisatie. Gebruik liever 'melkhuizen' voor aanvullende gebouwen voor de landbouw die vooral worden gebruikt voor de zorg voor melk, met weinig of geen mechanisatie.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>十九世紀早期開始興建的建築物，非僅見於農場內，供進行乳類及乳製品的機械化處理、儲存，或販賣。與「牛奶場（非機械化）」的差異在於機械化與否。而主要供生產牛奶用，通常機械化程度低，或不具機械設備之附屬農業建築，則較常稱為「牛奶房」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
